1. Package.json
    manifest file
        author
        name 
        version
        liscence
        dependencies
        
2. Jasmine
    (http://jasmine.github.io/edge/introduction.html)
    - Testing framework
        write tests (describe, it)
        expect - api for assertions
        jasmine spy -  mocking
        
3. Karma
    - framework for executing tests
    - run tests on different browsers

4. Protractor
    - framework for Browser testing
    
5. bower
    - manage clientside dependency for the application (angular, jquery etc)
    
Steps 
in the folder where the package.json
    run the command "npm install"